generated_description: fab chemicals, legally known as pychem-fab co., is a company based in coimbatore, tamil nadu, india. it specializes in the research, design, manufacturing, and distribution of high-quality construction chemicals. the company serves the construction industry in the middle east, africa, and india, and has expanded its network to include regions in europe and the far east. fab chemicals operates a state-of-the-art manufacturing facility in sharjah, united arab emirates, and collaborates with mix uk ltd. to produce a wide range of products, including waterproofing systems, concrete repair systems, protective coating systems, joint sealant systems, and more. the company adheres to international standards such as astm, din, and is, and is committed to providing technical support and quality products to enhance the performance and quality of structures.
